prompt.title: Embedding for 10 Essential Machine Learning Algorithms
prompt.content:
---

The document outlines 10 simple machine learning algorithms that beginners should know. These include:

1. Linear Regression
2. Logistic Regression
3. Linear Discriminant Analysis
4. Classification and Regression Trees
5. Naive Bayes
6. K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN)
7. Learning Vector Quantization (LVQ)
8. Support Vector Machines (SVM)
9. Bagging and Random Forest
10. Boosting and AdaBoost
